description = "Pack 256 sprite instances into a Float32Array, upload to a storage buffer, and submit one Renderer2D.drawInstancedSprites call. Each instance has its own position, rotation, and tint — the kind of batched UI / damage-number path the instanced sprite pipeline unlocks."

